# Citing TACC

## Recognizing TACC resources used in your research is vital for our funding.

Please reference TACC in any research report, journal or publication that requires citations. Recognition of TACC resources helps us acquire funding for the next generation of hardware, support services, research & development, visualization, data storage, and grid infrastructure.

### Suggested Citation

The authors acknowledge the Texas Advanced Computing Center (TACC) at The University of Texas at Austin for providing computational resources that have contributed to the research results reported within this paper. URL: <http://www.tacc.utexas.edu>

### Minimum Citation

Texas Advanced Computing Center (TACC) The University of Texas at Austin